messages.content: What does the ComfyUI_FastVAEDecoder_SDXL node allow you to do?
The ComfyUI_FastVAEDecoder_SDXL node allows users to quickly preview SDXL 1.0 latents.
What is the origin of the ComfyUI_FastVAEDecoder_SDXL node?
The ComfyUI_FastVAEDecoder_SDXL node is based on the repository at https://github.com/Birch-san/diffusers-play/tree/main/approx_vae.
Where can I see an example of the ComfyUI_FastVAEDecoder_SDXL node in action?
There are examples available in the GitHub repository, such as the fastVAE example and the original example, which can be viewed through the provided image links.
